{
  "stem": "27409.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I was called with the other two, three soldiers and sent to-- the commandant wants to speak to us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he said, you are good soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Look, you have here an order to go to Rovno.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That is in Volhynia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He said, in Russia, you don't go by Rolls-Royce, and so you-- you thought you find a carriage, a truck which goes the direction you're taking.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And you-- so I went to Rovno.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In Rovno, I announced myself to Commandant [INAUDIBLE] that I was nearly killed because the Stukas appeared and bombed us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I didn't know where to run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I was laying near some tanks with one of the-- my friends from the old-- old-- old unit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We, again, tried to eat in the house which was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "What happened, happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when I turned my head towards him-- we were speaking-- his head was gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You can imagine sitting in-- in Rovno or where.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "When they came back, they gave me an order to go again for [NON-ENGLISH] in Volodymyr-Volynskyi.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "From Volodymyr-Volynskyi, they had a-- a unit which was formed in the forest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That was a special unit, a special commando unit from special operation behind the front and on the front line.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So I reached my 81st military special [INAUDIBLE] unit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "With this I stood, I was, up to the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Up to-- from my killing, if I could call it so, when I was brought from the peasant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in November 1942 up to, uh, '43, 1943 in March, when I came back to Chernovitz, the liberation of Chernovitz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, '44, sorry, '44, it was. '44 because we were operating the whole summer with them. '44, it was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over a year.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One and a half year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
